OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry through the evening and overnight.
OL,7,FSome prolonged spells of evening
OL,8,Fsunshine leading to some clear spells
OL,9,Fovernight meaning it might feel chilly
OL,10,Fin places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FDry with lengthy bright or
OL,13,Fsunny spells and feeling slightly
OL,14,Fwarmer. Sunshine turning hazy later as
OL,15,Fhigh cloud spreads southeast. Cloudier
OL,16,Fwith the odd spot of rain in the
OL,17,Fevening.
